
FNF Agent Stack
SOAP Troubleshooting Guide

Symptom  |  Observation  |  Action  |  Prevention

Mark R. Bracking  |  funnynfunny.com  |  Version 1.0  |  March 2026

How to Use This Guide
Each card covers one error using the SOAP format:

Letter
Stands For
What It Tells You
S
Symptom
What the error looks like — the exact message or behaviour you see
O
Observation
What is actually happening underneath — the root cause
A
Action
Step-by-step fix — follow in order
P
Prevention
How to stop this happening again


Each card also shows which agent is affected in brackets: [All Agents], [Agent 1], [Agent 2], or [Agent 3].

